(2835, 3, '2015-10-14 00:35:19', '2015-10-14 00:35:19', 'As you know, an exciting initiative is underway in Ontario to support students as they integrate robotics into the Ontario curriculum and further the development of 21st century learning skills. \n\nAs part of the Ministry of Educations initiatives to engage pupils in innovative and forward-thinking activities, all 72 Ontario school boards are receiving robotic kits this fall (2015).  CODE is acting on behalf of the Ministry to organize and manage distribution of these kits throughout the province.\n\nThe robotics program began this past summer with test projects as part of the 2015 CODE Summer Learning Program. One major aim is to engage students in the development of 21st century skills and competencies through the use of robotics and associated activities. \n\nWith this early link between summer learning and robotics already established, it seems appropriate to continue sharing resources, ideas and discussions around the use of robotics in the classroom here on CODEs Summer Learning robotics forum.We welcome your thoughts on how robotics can stimulate and enrich student learning, and invite you to share your experiences and success stories relating to the use of robotics in your boards classrooms.\n\nRobotics-related resources and articles shared here will also be posted in this websites <a href="http://ontariosummerlearning.org/resource-tag/robotics/" target="_blank">Robotics</a> section. Your contributions will help build greater understanding of the connections between robotics/STEM resources and the creation of learning opportunities and environments for students to acquire important competencies such as critical thinking, communication, collaboration and creativity.\n\nSo welcome to the Robotics community! If you have any questions about contributing/accessing content, please contact the Summer Learning website coordinator, Jeff Dunk, at <a href="mailto:jdunk@opsoa.org" target="_blank">jdunk@opsoa.org</a>.\n\n- Gerry Townsend\n', 'Your invitation to join the robotics discussion, from CODEs Gerry Townsend.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'your-invitation-to-join-the-robotics-discussion-from-codes-gerry-townsend', '', '', '2015-10-14 00:35:19', '2015-10-14 00:35:19', '', 2253, 'http://ontariosummerlearning.org/forums/topic/your-invitation-to-join-the-robotics-discussion-from-codes-gerry-townsend/', 0, 'topic', '', 0);
